<h3 id="2-organising-attributes">2. Organising attributes</h3>

<p>Spend a minute as a group observing and clarifying the results of the above. As moderators, take fresh post-it notes and cluster similar ideas into high-level themes. Confirm with participants and then make it real by naming each theme.</p>

<p>An example: post-it notes take from different categories such as â€˜warmâ€™, â€˜dependableâ€™, â€˜wiseâ€™, and â€˜role-modelâ€™ might be themed as â€˜Guiding Lightâ€™.</p>

