<h3 id="3-creating-brand-attributes">3. Creating brand attributes</h3>

<p>For each of your new themes, and openly as a group, list attributes under the following areas:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Symbol</li>
  <li>Typography</li>
  <li>Photography</li>
  <li>Illustration</li>
  <li>Colour</li>
  <li>Motion</li>
  <li>Graphic forms</li>
  <li>Sound</li>
  <li>Language</li>
</ul>

<p>Attributes from the Metamorphosis exercises can be recycled.</p>

<p>Stop when you feel attribute additions slowing or becoming worse in quality. Use this as your cutting off pointâ€”play back the group-created attributes to the participants to seal the deal.</p>

